<figureCitation box="[431,499,1899,1925]" captionStart="FIGURES 3–8" captionStartId="3.[151,264,1376,1400]" captionTargetBox="[183,1382,200,1325]" captionTargetId="figure-308@3.[166,1413,176,1345]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURES 3–8. Adults of Ripeacma spp. 3, R. anisopenis sp. nov.; 4, R. apicilispina sp. nov.; 5, R. bihamatilis sp. nov.; 6, R. bitriangulata sp. nov.; 7, R. dissectaedeaga sp. nov.; 8, R. magnimaculata sp. nov. All holotypes and males, except paratype and female for R. anisophylla. Scales = 1.00 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6911453" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6911453/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="523">Fig. 3</figureCitation>
